<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PIXEL WORLD - Real-time Pixel World</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: #0d0d12;
            color: #fff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        
        /* Premium Background Gradients */
        .bg-blob {
            position: absolute;
            width: 600px;
            height: 600px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(100px);
            opacity: 0.5;
            z-index: -1;
            animation: float 20s infinite ease-in-out alternate;
        }
        .blob-1 { background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,0,127,0.4) 0%, rgba(127,0,255,0) 70%); top: -100px; left: -100px; }
        .blob-2 { background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,127,255,0.4) 0%, rgba(0,255,127,0) 70%); bottom: -100px; right: -100px; animation-delay: -10s; }

        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
            100% { transform: translate(50px, 50px) scale(1.1); }
        }

        /* Navbar */
        nav {
            padding: 20px 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff007f, #7f00ff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }
        .nav-links a {
            color: #e2e2e2;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        .nav-links a:hover { color: #fff; }

        /* Hero */
        main {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 80px;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            letter-spacing: -3px;
        }
        .text-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff007f, #00d2ff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #a0a0b0;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .btn-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .btn {
            padding: 16px 40px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff007f, #7f00ff);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 0, 127, 0.3);
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(255, 0, 127, 0.5);
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="bg-blob blob-1"></div>
    <div class="bg-blob blob-2"></div>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo">PIXEL WORLD</div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/login">Login</a>
            <a href="/register">Register</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <h1>Leave your mark<br>on the <span class="text-gradient">World</span>.</h1>
        <p>A completely free, open-source collaborative canvas mapped to the real globe. Join thousands of users in shaping our planet pixel by pixel.</p>
        <div class="btn-group">
            <a href="/map" class="btn btn-primary">Open Canvas</a>
            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-secondary">Create Account</a>
        </div>
    </main>

</body>
</html>